class ThreadMain
{
	public static void main(String args[])
	{
		System.out.println("Lets find out the current Thread");
		Thread t = Thread.currentThread();
		System.out.println("Current Thread ="+t);
		System.out.println("Its name = "+t.getName());
	}
}


Output - 
Lets find out the current Thread
Current Thread =Thread[main,5,main]
Its name = main


Here CurrentThread() is static method in Thread class used to get the current thread.
